<h4 id="attention-is-all-you-need-1">attention is all you need</h4>]]></content><author><name>Oh WonTaek</name></author><category term="Paper" /><category term="transformer" /><category term="attention" /><category term="positional_encoding" /><category term="embedding" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Word Embedding & Positional Encoding]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">[Github Markdown] 깃허브 마크다운 문법</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/blog/github-markdown/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="[Github Markdown] 깃허브 마크다운 문법" /><published>2023-04-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-04-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/blog/github-markdown</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/blog/github-markdown/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="header-star-star-star">Header :star: :star: :star:</h2>
<p><strong>글의 제목</strong><br />
제목들은 <u>Contents</u> 에 자동으로 등록된다</p>
