<span class="o">&gt;</span>
<span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">Thats</span> <span class="n">so</span> <span class="n">funny</span><span class="err">!</span> <span class="p">:</span><span class="n">joy</span><span class="p">:</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<blockquote>
  <p>Gone camping! :tent: Be back soon.</p>

  <p>Thats so funny! :joy:</p>
</blockquote>

