<h2 id="math-supportlatex-star-star-star-star-star">Math support(latex) :star: :star: :star: :star: :star:</h2>
<p>github는 원래 수식을 작성하는 latex를 지원하지 않았다.<br />
22년 5월부터 latex를 지원한다고 한다. <a href="https://github.blog/2022-05-19-math-support-in-markdown/">https://github.blog/2022-05-19-math-support-in-markdown/</a></p>
<blockquote>
  <p>한줄 전체에 적용되는 $$ latex formula $$</p>

  <p>인라인수식은 $ inline formula $</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-cpp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">$$\</span><span class="n">frac</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">}{</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="err">\</span><span class="n">sum_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="n">Q_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">K_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="err">$$</span>  
<span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">RNN</span><span class="err">의</span> <span class="n">hidden</span> <span class="n">state</span><span class="err">는</span> <span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">h_t</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">f_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">w</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">h_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">t</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">},</span> <span class="n">x_</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">t</span><span class="p">})</span> <span class="err">$</span> <span class="err">입니다</span><span class="p">.</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>$\frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^{n} Q_{i} * K_{i}$$<br />
RNN의 hidden state는 $ h_t = f_{w} (h_{t-1}, x_{t}) $ 입니다.</p>

